{"word":"προνομή","slug":"προνομή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προνομή</b></el> <el>(προνομή, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:προνέμω'><el>προνέμω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a foraging, a foraging expedition, foray</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>: in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a>, <i>foraging parties</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>an elephant's trunk</i>, <b><a href='S:Polybius'>Polyb.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b>= <el>προ-νομία</el>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}